text: Didik Wahyu Wijayance (born February 13, 1994) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Liga 1 club Persikabo 1973. ==Career== ===Persikabo 1973=== He started playing professionally with Persikabo 1973 in 2018. == References == ==External links== * Didik Wahyu at Soccerway * Didik Wahyu at Liga Indonesia Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Persikabo 1973 players Category:Association football defenders
